					<description><![CDATA[As we described when we kicked off this quarters UK project to map petrol stations, recent community validation of third party (import) data has highlighted much outdated and erroneous data within OpenStreetMap :-(. For the Shell import we captured some &#8230; <a href="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2018/01/petrol-stations-with-a-fixme-tag.html">Continued</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>As we <a href="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2018/01/q1-2018-mapping-project-petrol-stations.html">described</a> when we kicked off this quarters UK project to map petrol stations, recent community validation of third party (import) data has highlighted much outdated and erroneous data within OpenStreetMap :-(. For the Shell import we captured some of this and added it to a &#8220;fixme&#8221; tag. If you have not yet come across this tag then it is one in which OpenStreetMap users can flag something that looks wrong or requires additional information to improve the map.</p>
<p>It is possible to view petrol stations with a fixme tag by using Overpass Turbo scripts. We have done this already so all you have to do is click <a href="https://overpass-turbo.eu/s/uZD">this link</a> and press run. Results are visual as shown in the example below. There are approximately 130 petrol stations with a fixme tag so with some effort we should be able to review them all. Happy mapping!</p>
<div id="attachment_1526" style="width: 827px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1526" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1526 size-full" src="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/petrol_fixme.png" alt="" width="817" height="421" srcset="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/petrol_fixme.png 817w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/petrol_fixme-300x155.png 300w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/petrol_fixme-768x396.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 817px) 100vw, 817px" /><p id="caption-attachment-1526" class="wp-caption-text">Example result from Overpass Turbo.</p></div>
]]></content:encoded>
					
