<p>So far this year we have visited Stratford-upon-Avon where we attempted to map all the tourist accommodation (it is the 400th annivarsary of Shakespeare&#8217;s death and this town is a global tourist destination). The ongoing project is to map all the buildings &#8211; help appreciated!</p>
